data.description: ***YEAR END INCENTIVE! $22,500 TO LOWER RATE, PRICE, OR CLOSING COSTS***    Welcome to 529 Peace Pipe Way in Georgetown, TX! This elegant single-family residence in the sought-after Riverview community offers modern features and stylish design, complemented by captivating long-distance views! With 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathroom, this home provides a spacious and comfortable living space for you and your family.  Step inside and be greeted by an open floorplan filled with natural light and high ceilings. The living room boasts abundant space, creating a vibrant atmosphere, while the vinyl flooring in the main areas adds a touch of contemporary flair. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with a kitchen island, stainless steel appliances.  Keep your kitchen organized with the convenience of a pantry. The primary bedroom, situated on the main level, is your personal retreat, featuring a high ceiling, ceiling fan, and a tranquil ensuite bathroom with a separate shower and soaking tub, double vanity, and walk-in closet. This home is equipped with smart features, allowing you to effortlessly control various aspects of your home. Step outside to the private yard, ideal for outdoor gatherings or simply relaxing and enjoying the picturesque views. The Riverview community offers fantastic amenities, including a park, greenbelt areas, San Gabriel River access, and a pool, making leisurely activities a delightful experience. Take advantage of the sidewalks and trails for pleasant walks, jogs, or bike rides. Conveniently located in Georgetown's Riverview neighborhood, this home is close to schools, shopping centers, and dining options, ensuring all your needs are within reach. With easy access to major roads, commuting is a breeze. Embrace a life of comfort and convenience in this remarkable Riverview residence!
